gifts.like: All Universal Likes, All Eggs (except Void Egg)
gifts.neutral: All Universal Neutrals, All Fruit (except Fruit Tree Fruit & Salmonberry), All Milk, Common Mushroom, Daffodil, Dandelion, Ginger, Hazelnut, Leek, Magna Cap, Morel, Purple Mushroom, Snow Yam, Winter Root,

heart_events.2h: On a sunny summer day, visit the beach when Alex is there.
heart_events.5h: Enter Alex's house when he's there
heart_events.6h: Enter Alex's house when he's there
heart_events.8h: On a sunny day, visit the beach when Alex is there. He is only scheduled to go to the beach in summer, but may pass by on the way to the Ginger Island resort in any season after it is completed.
heart_events.10h: Alex will send you a letter to meet him at the Saloon after dark. After receiving the letter, enter the Saloon between 7pm and 10pm.
heart_events.14h: Exit the Farmhouse in year 2+ between 6am and 8:20am on any day other than Sunday. You must have 5,000g available.
